OL,3,CBelfast City Hall lit up in purple to
OL,4,Cmark Holocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,FTo mark Holocaust Memorial Day,
OL,7,FBelfast City Hall was illuminated in
OL,8,Fpurple on Saturday.
OL,10,FThe 27th January is the date on which
OL,11,Fthe former Nazi concentration and
OL,12,Fextermination camp, Auschwitz-Birkenau
OL,13,Fwas liberated in 1945.
OL,15,FOne million jewish people were
OL,16,Fmurdered there out of an estimated six
OL,17,Fmillion in total.
OL,19,FThe theme for the 2024 Holocaust
OL,20,FMemorial Day (HND) was "Fragility of
OL,21,FFreedom".
