OL,3,CBelfast City Hall lit up in purple to
OL,4,Cmark Holocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,F"We can all reflect on how freedom is
OL,7,Ffragile and vulnerable to abuse," said
OL,8,Fthe HMD Trust.
OL,10,F"As we come together in communities
OL,11,Faround the UK, let's pledge not to
OL,12,Ftake our freedoms for granted, and
OL,13,Fconsider what we can do to strengthen
OL,14,Ffreedoms around the world."
OL,16,FA Regional Commemoration was hosted by
OL,17,FThe Executive Office earlier in the
OL,18,Fweek.
