OL,3,CBelfast City Hall lit up in purple to
OL,4,Cmark Holocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,FIn conjunction with the HMD Trust and
OL,7,FBelfast City Council, an event on
OL,8,FTuesday heard from Holocaust survivor
OL,9,FDr Alfred Garwood, who spoke movingly
OL,10,Fabout the collective trauma felt by
OL,11,Fsurvivors after their freedoms had
OL,12,Fbeen stripped away.
OL,14,FDr Garwood, who along with his family
OL,15,Fwas interned at the Bergen-Belsen
OL,16,Fconcentration camp from 1943 - 1945,
OL,17,Fsaid: "I feel honoured and humbled to
OL,18,Fbe asked to speak in Belfast for
OL,19,FHolocaust Memorial Day.
