OL,3,CBelfast City Hall lit up in purple to
OL,4,Cmark Holocaust Memorial Day
OL,6,F"Being a Holocaust Survivor, later a
OL,7,Fphysician, a psychiatrist and a
OL,8,Fpsychotherapist, having endured the
OL,9,Ftroubled times of the Second World War
OL,10,Fand the Holocaust it has taught me to
OL,11,Frecognise the suffering of communities
OL,12,Fwho have endured generations of
OL,13,Fconflict.
OL,15,F"I believe the Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fcommunity have shown great courage and
OL,17,Fcreativity in working towards,
OL,18,Fmaintaining and protecting their
OL,19,Fprecious and fragile freedom and
OL,20,Fpeace."
